Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-dono! I am glad!\NI am glad that you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the night of the Fire Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:23.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,after finding out their crewmate,\N Kanjuro, was an enemy informant,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:28.01,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it seemed like all hope\Nfor the Akazaya samurai was lost,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Luffy and the other pirates\Ncame through for them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's Luffy's clan here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only them, I heard Law was jailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-dono, I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan was all leaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we fight without them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one more thing that we haven't told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NWe didn't want to plunge you into further despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's banquet isn't just another banquet\Non the night of the Fire Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also a banquet to celebrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...the alliance between us, the Animal Kingdom Pirates,\Nand the infamous Big Mom Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! The competition is on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bounce-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Injection Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kyoshiro Family's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoshiro's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Good Luck?!\NLeader Kin'emon's Plot!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Boss-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to sink the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've only disabled the cannon\Npointed at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! He's quite skillful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the Shogun's dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a yakuza\Nwho's taking the place of Boss Hyogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Akazaya samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a yakuza from the Flower Capital,\Npeople call me Napping Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My Kyoshiro Family is 200 strong\Nand we would like to help you with your raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--You've got to be kidding, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he want to join our side?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He was supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?! You're Orochi's subordinate!\NWhat favor do you owe us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe the Kozuki Clan\Nan immeasurable number of favors and debts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I often remember you, Kin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mountain God incident\Nthat occurred in the capital 40 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,People thought that was\Njust Oden-sama going crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That happened because the younger you\Nwho was so greedy tried to sell a little boar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Paradise Waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one person left\Nwho knows that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they call it the Mountain God!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! It's my fault that the capital is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Denjiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Denjiro-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Denjiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too many enemies...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a hand, Ashura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Denjiro! Ashura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance, Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take over the future of the Kozuki\Nand Oden-sama's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That is right! I am the Kozuki Clan's retainer\Nand one of the Akazaya Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Denjiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I am unrecognizable...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When I learned of Kin-san and the others' return,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to come forward right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I remained an enemy, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, if I had revealed my identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the spy would've blown my cover\Nand I would've been wiped out by Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Denjiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However, since I continued to earn\NOrochi's trust until the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to free the 1,000 samurai\Nin Rasetsu Town Prisoners' Quarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--Look over there!\N--Reinforcements for the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Those symbols are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai clan crests!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,1,200 soldiers in total! Count us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This day's finally come! We get to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss Kyoshiro is one of the Akazaya Nine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Onigashima now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Denjiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hell of a smart man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This symbol implying the date\Nand the rendezvous point for the great battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two birds on fire and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...a {\i0}Habu{\i1} (pit viper) and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...a Reversed Crescent Moon\Nwhich signifies rebellion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"On the day of the Fire Festival.\NTwilight - the second hour of the bird.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At Habu Port."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The original symbol didn't have those two lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This flyer was leaked to Orochi and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but Yasuie-sama altered it\Nbefore he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,These two newly-added lines mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...crossing out the middle letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the new rendezvous point is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:50.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}HABUMINATO{\i0} (HABU PORT)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Habuminato{\i0} (Habu Port) without the middle part...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...which is {\i1}hato{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.82,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}HATO{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}HATO{\i0} (WHARF)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the wharf at Habu Port which has a great view of the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,maple tree forest that Yasuie-sama loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing two lines on a {\i1}habu{\i0} (pit viper),\Nanyone would easily get the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, sensing that Orochi's spy was with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,purposefully told your people\Nthat it was "Tokage Port"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Every port in the Land of Wano\Nhas a name that sounds the same as an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is a bit too long,\Nbut adding limbs to a {\i1}habu{\i0} snake makes it a lizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokage (Lizard) Port is in Udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, that picture didn't look like a lizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed it\Nbecause Kin-sama was so confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The spy fell right into your trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and told Orochi\Nthat Tokage Port was the new rendezvous point!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the foolishness of the one\Nwho acted as he liked in the capital for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi misjudged the distance between each place\Nand didn't do anything until last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to show you hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--{\i1}Did you find the ship?{\i0}\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,GREAT BRIDGE BETWEEN KIBI AND UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,GREAT BRIDGE BETWEEN KURI AND UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,GREAT BRIDGE BETWEEN RINGO AND HAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,ITACHI PORT, KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But by that time,\Neveryone had crossed those great bridges,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ships they needed had left the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All that was destroyed were leftover ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you planned,\Nthe 4,200 troops that you recruited...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...were lying low at the Habu Port wharf\Nuntil the time came!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, are they all safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after 20 years,\NI still remember Oden-sama's legendary death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We have lived our lives\Nbelieving in the Kozuki Clan's comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We are coming with you, Akazaya samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We are fully ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan to raid Onigashima\Nhasn't gone wrong at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Adding the 1,200 of us,\Nit's 5,400 in total!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To Onigashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tons of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!\NAnything from Onigashima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been calling them, but they haven't noticed\Nsince they're busy with the banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that trouble,\Nwe ended up with more allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We were gonna do it anyway though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--The greater the force the better.\N--It's good to have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can easily beat the Animal Kingdom Pirates now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spectacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know what happened,\Nbut everything's alright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lower your guard.\NBig Mom is at Onigashima, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no! Nothing has changed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn you, Kin'emon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin-san! That's our leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worthy of respect as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Kin'emon-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can lead us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll follow you to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it wasn't " {\i0}tokage {\i1}(lizard)"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was " {\i0}hato{\i1} (wharf)"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest, Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you're not capable of\Ntelling such a clever lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned out to be all right.\NWe won't get mad so say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You really thought it was "{\i1}tokage{\i0}," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it turned out fine after all!\NIt was a lucky mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll die in this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've used up a lifetime's worth of luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're stunningly lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--Kin'emon-dono!\N--Our beloved leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But since we share the same goal,\Nit was our luck, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, Kin-sama!\NWe won't let you die alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We served Oden-sama together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We were born and raised differently,\Nbut we'll die together! Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not happy to hear it\Nfrom annoying men like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your sword, Kin-san!\NWe know we'll win this preliminary skirmish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept my fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been 20 years\Nsince Oden-sama's tragic death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Land of Wano has been in a darkness\Ndarker than this cloudy sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But the time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to Onigashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's avenge Oden-sama's death together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna change the Land of Wano\Nat any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let's retreat for now!\N--O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,--What's this?!\N--What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--What are we gonna do?!\N--We've got to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can go home safely\Nafter you mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We don't need to go after them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Kin'emon...\NI have to report to Onigashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I fulfilled my role that Orochi-{\i1}sama {\i0}gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just one thing left to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamatsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not know\Nyou were this good at drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you kidnap Momonosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamatsu! I am coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! You'll drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have shared\Nmany years of pain and suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We served under Oden-sama together\Nand we lost him together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you enjoy deceiving\Nand betraying such friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you enjoy trampling on our wishes\Nand disappointing us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm having so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Deception, subterfuge, and then a surprise ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no role in the world\Nthat's more worthwhile than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how you guys played the fool, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll end the play by staining the stage\Nwith the Kozuki's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Momonosuke.\NI'll let your sister follow you into death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:22:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamatsu!\NI swear I'll find Hiyori and kill her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she's alive now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe you drew a bird\Nthat flies so beautifully!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All we saw were ugly and useless drawings\Nthat dissolved in water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was part of my acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me down! I am scared! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We sank them at the same time again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sink the last ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let me do it!\N--I said I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanjuro? Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you're no match for Kaido-sama's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.36,0:22:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even enter the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.01,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As he is taken away,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:22.84,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the young general Momonosuke endures his trembling fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.84,Italics,,0,0,0,,shouts his heart out and encourages his friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:30.01,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enraged at Kanjuro's betrayal, the Straw Hats blow away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,the enemy's attack along with the rough waves!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:36.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll save their friend at any cost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"A Tearful Promise! The Kidnapped Momonosuke!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:48.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,
